 web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/terms\">\"Facebook Terms of Agreement\"</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Facebook+Terms+of+Agreement&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fterms&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACommunication+ethics\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">NCA. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://commethics.org/news/\">\"Communication Ethics Division\"</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Communication+Ethics+Division&amp;rft.au=NCA&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fcommethics.org%2Fnews%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACommunication+ethics\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://wmich.edu/ethics/docs/85_newsletter.pdf\">\"SCA Communication Ethics Commission - Newsletter\"</a> <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(PDF)</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=SCA+Communication+Ethics+Commission+-+Newsletter&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwmich.edu%2Fethics%2Fdocs%2F85_newsletter.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACommunication+ethics\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">^</a></b></span> <sp